Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.08,0:02:33.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被選擇的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.94,0:01:48.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.60,0:01:50.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.30,0:01:56.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這個鎮上的鎮民
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.90,0:01:58.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不自量力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.32,0:02:01.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然敢攻打我的城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.08,0:02:03.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對他們施了秘術
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.25,0:02:06.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的他們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.06,0:02:10.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成了我隨心所欲操縱的部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.55,0:02:13.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想對這些人動手嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.67,0:02:15.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.83,0:02:49.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想對那些鎮民發動攻擊的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.87,0:02:51.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就把那些疼痛化成數倍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.02,0:02:54.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓那些小丫頭們也感受一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.00,0:02:55.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.95,0:02:59.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.05,0:03:20.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反擊看看啊  小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.87,0:03:28.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  已經不行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.20,0:03:30.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.10,0:03:39.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  抓緊一點  黑碰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.28,0:03:42.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落在後面就別指責我了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.92,0:03:59.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然  只要有這根羽毛在手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.38,0:04:00.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是無敵的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.94,0:04:05.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼  小狼  振作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.06,0:04:07.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.40,0:04:11.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.50,0:04:13.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.43,0:04:19.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.75,0:04:23.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後可以不叫你「小狼君」  而叫「小狼」行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.73,0:04:27.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不好  小狼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.73,0:04:31.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.60,0:04:33.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.34,0:04:44.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是…秘術吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.94,0:04:45.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.31,0:04:49.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩個人…是假的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.06,0:04:52.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡…胡說什麼啊  那當然是真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.51,0:04:56.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的…公主她…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.41,0:05:09.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不會再叫我「小狼」了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.19,0:05:14.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  遊戲就到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.18,0:05:22.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.10,0:05:27.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.59,0:05:30.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點給我收拾掉那個小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.50,0:05:40.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.38,0:05:43.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清醒過來吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.50,0:05:53.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.55,0:06:12.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.50,0:06:13.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.13,0:06:16.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我們會在這種地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.74,0:06:17.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.44,0:06:22.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.76,0:06:24.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你們都一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.82,0:06:26.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都被那傢伙的秘術控制了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.64,0:06:30.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是多虧春香救了我們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.88,0:06:32.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是只憑我自己一人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.02,0:06:34.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有母親
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.59,0:06:37.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這面鏡子是母親的秘術道具
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.50,0:06:39.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.49,0:06:42.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的力量還很薄弱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.43,0:06:45.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我對這面鏡子發誓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.12,0:06:47.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓你這種人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.34,0:06:49.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來限制大家的自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.46,0:06:50.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.88,0:06:54.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  請在外面集結部隊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.41,0:06:55.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.26,0:06:58.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就交給我們好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.91,0:07:00.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.85,0:07:05.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…真是倒霉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.06,0:07:08.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真可憐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.03,0:07:13.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這個聲音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.07,0:07:37.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  趕上了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.74,0:07:38.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.43,0:07:39.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.54,0:07:41.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.91,0:07:43.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊也遇上了很多麻煩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.62,0:07:47.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把羽毛  還回來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.23,0:07:55.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是小櫻公主的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.05,0:07:57.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還回來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.41,0:07:59.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼君…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.65,0:08:03.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢…慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.40,0:08:06.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果用這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.59,0:08:09.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許能讓春香的母親復活…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.27,0:08:15.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.15,0:08:17.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果打倒了我的話  就沒法做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.91,0:08:22.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.32,0:08:25.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很想念媽媽吧  想見到媽媽吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.07,0:08:29.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這股強大的力量的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.67,0:08:30.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.98,0:08:34.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能讓你的母親…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.28,0:08:37.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你殺死的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.50,0:08:40.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了想保護這座城鎮的母親…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.55,0:08:42.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親說過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.43,0:08:44.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管使用怎樣的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.49,0:08:47.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去的生命是回不來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.57,0:08:53.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論多麼懷念的人  再怎麼想見到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.12,0:08:57.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也已經見不到母親了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.75,0:08:58.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  不要忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.89,0:09:04.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽會一直在你身邊注視著你的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.93,0:09:08.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…所以你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:11.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在那裡胡說…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.99,0:09:12.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.58,0:09:17.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要報仇嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.74,0:09:23.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那樣能平息你的內心的話也好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.95,0:09:25.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.69,0:09:29.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種男人是值得讓春香來動手的人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.25,0:09:37.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘術是一種能給人帶來幸福的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.89,0:09:49.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種傢伙  我不屑跟他動手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.71,0:10:01.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別…別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.92,0:10:03.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不要碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.06,0:10:15.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.84,0:11:11.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那位大姐的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.33,0:11:13.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡可以信任她  沒問題的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.20,0:11:16.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個男人就交給我處理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.61,0:11:18.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得好好向他道謝才行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.97,0:11:23.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然敢把我關在這種城堡裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.97,0:11:25.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我秘妖的國度裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.95,0:11:28.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和你兒子會受到最高的待遇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.97,0:11:31.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.67,0:11:34.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香就是你嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.08,0:11:35.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.26,0:11:39.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的媽媽是優秀的秘術師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.05,0:11:43.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然由於這個領主的卑鄙陷阱而過世  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.51,0:11:47.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在與我的戰鬥中磨練自己
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.41,0:11:51.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說過希望你能成為超越她的秘術師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.72,0:11:53.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待你長大之後啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.73,0:12:02.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變強吧  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.79,0:12:06.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要像過世的媽媽一樣強到足以用秘術和我一決高下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.41,0:12:09.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.45,0:12:14.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.46,0:12:18.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.75,0:12:20.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.45,0:12:24.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.92,0:12:26.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可愛的小傢伙們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.06,0:12:28.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.67,0:12:44.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢復了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.89,0:12:48.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就…結束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.69,0:12:56.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.66,0:13:27.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日快樂  小櫻公主
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.85,0:13:29.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  雪兔哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.24,0:13:34.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點東西對這麼大胃口的人來說  恐怕不夠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.29,0:13:36.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼多  我根本吃不了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.32,0:13:37.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  你可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.38,0:13:40.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  別鬧了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.48,0:13:42.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼多我根本吃不了  真的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.93,0:13:43.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.93,0:13:44.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.41,0:13:47.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  這可是特製料理
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.55,0:13:48.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.69,0:13:53.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廚師說今天的點心是他的得意作品呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.51,0:13:57.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是專門為生日製作的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.18,0:13:58.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.01,0:14:03.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城裡的廚師做的點心真的很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.50,0:14:08.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.06,0:14:11.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天很感謝你能來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.56,0:14:13.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.67,0:14:17.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的生日能和…一起過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.37,0:14:21.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的真的好高興
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.96,0:14:35.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.45,0:14:37.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明…沒有人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.01,0:14:50.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽毛…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.46,0:14:53.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有一根…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.44,0:14:55.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿回來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.39,0:15:18.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.46,0:15:21.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會把你們送到住在另一個世界的人那裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.31,0:15:27.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.43,0:15:33.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  準備走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.20,0:15:35.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到魔女的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.76,0:15:44.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.62,0:15:47.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說過想要變強
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.22,0:15:52.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在這個國家  再也沒有比你更強的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.03,0:15:55.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此要把你送去異界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.09,0:15:58.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切！這不是單純的推卸嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.17,0:16:03.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  祝你一路順風了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.15,0:16:06.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  給我記住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.23,0:16:13.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有前往異世界的力量的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.36,0:16:14.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早已存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.04,0:16:20.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  深埋在那個玖樓國地底下的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.17,0:16:22.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,具有遠超越於其上的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.37,0:16:25.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在  正在孕育的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.16,0:16:28.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠改變世界的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.52,0:16:32.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了得到那股力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.75,0:16:34.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我耗費了漫長的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.59,0:16:49.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要…得到手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.38,0:17:03.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎還輪不到你出場呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.35,0:17:06.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.69,0:17:11.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會因為你而覺醒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.11,0:17:14.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前並不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.41,0:17:20.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  大家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.78,0:17:23.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在可以慶祝打倒領主了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.53,0:17:25.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡情狂歡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.60,0:17:38.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.18,0:17:40.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推翻了領主
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.22,0:17:42.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼都沒做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.10,0:17:44.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那座城的秘術沒有解開的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.14,0:17:47.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就永遠也沒辦法接近了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.60,0:17:49.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  這是小狼你們的功勞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.77,0:17:51.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我真的沒什麼功勞…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.23,0:17:54.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑Ｐ也是大活躍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.59,0:17:55.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.51,0:17:58.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  幫我修好了房頂  幫忙了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.19,0:17:59.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.30,0:18:05.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於羽毛又找回了一根
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.14,0:18:09.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻看上去更開朗一些了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.39,0:18:10.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.14,0:18:14.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  春香給我們的療傷藥很有用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.33,0:18:18.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是母親以前所製作的藥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.86,0:18:20.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我還沒辦法做出來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.00,0:18:24.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我會努力成為一個不讓母親蒙羞的秘術師
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.65,0:18:31.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.36,0:18:34.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.29,0:18:40.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於…到達鎮上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.29,0:18:42.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.03,0:18:47.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是暗行御使
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.36,0:18:49.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  別騙人了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.26,0:18:53.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,政府派來的暗行御使就只是這種小孩嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.16,0:18:54.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水戶黃門啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.30,0:18:58.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  誰是小助  誰是小格啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.33,0:19:02.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷糊彌七呢  陽炎八兵衛呢  風車阿銀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.58,0:19:02.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在說什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.93,0:19:03.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.74,0:19:05.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  證明身份的印盒呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.97,0:19:08.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.41,0:19:12.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…暗行御使的紋章？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.88,0:19:18.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是藍色紋章啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.03,0:19:19.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.73,0:19:22.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自顧自的在做什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.60,0:19:24.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正值這樣的年紀而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.35,0:19:28.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…真的是小孩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.70,0:19:32.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,領主似乎把突然得到手的大部分力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.56,0:19:35.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用在這座城鎮外面施展了結界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.46,0:19:37.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於這個結界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.06,0:19:43.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有秘術的人都無法進入鎮裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.46,0:19:46.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過現在結界消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.29,0:19:48.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於能夠進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.16,0:19:57.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們來遲了  真的是十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.56,0:20:01.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些傷口…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.06,0:20:05.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們為了能進鎮裡來  費了很大的力氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.88,0:20:09.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與你們所忍受的痛苦比起來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.90,0:20:11.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在算不上什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.33,0:20:17.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們能來  真是謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.81,0:20:19.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用卑鄙手段成為領主的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.93,0:20:21.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來已經不存在了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.66,0:20:23.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須選出新的領主來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.58,0:20:30.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不需要新的領主了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.05,0:20:37.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓮姬將由大家齊心協力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.29,0:20:39.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而成為比任何地方都要美麗的城鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.95,0:20:49.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以請教一下嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.79,0:20:54.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為旅行者的你們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.93,0:20:58.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不惜把自己性命置之度外而拯救城鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.24,0:21:03.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起來種花
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.34,0:21:05.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓城鎮變得更加漂亮起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.40,0:21:10.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  為什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.46,0:21:12.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.51,0:21:20.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後的事就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.14,0:21:42.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝了  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.53,0:21:45.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在也該要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.99,0:21:48.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  你們要去哪裡呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.27,0:21:55.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩可拿·摩多基正興奮不已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.85,0:22:04.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼  為什麼會長出翅膀來呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.34,0:22:09.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們明明才剛來這裡的…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.56,0:22:13.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們有非做不可的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.91,0:22:16.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保重了  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.39,0:22:36.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.26,0:22:38.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.01,0:22:43.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有緣再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.70,0:22:45.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天…一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.88,0:22:54.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝了  大家
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.48,0:24:34.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到達了新的世界囉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.54,0:24:36.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次也是個神奇的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.19,0:24:38.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森林裡雖然有一個湖
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.79,0:24:40.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而鎮子和人之類的卻通通沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.83,0:24:43.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這裡卻有著羽毛的氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.50,0:24:47.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？小狼和小櫻是如何相遇的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.71,0:24:49.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就請繼續期待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.54,0:24:50.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翼·年代記
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.85,0:24:53.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十二話  溫暖的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.33,0:24:56.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回摩可拿的模仿術會讓人期待不已


